Direct Answer
Non-volatile case: All four outputs are possible:
(0,0), (0,1), (1,0), (1,1)

Volatile case: Only three outputs are possible:
(0,1), (1,0), (1,1)
The output (0,0) is impossible due to happens-before constraints from volatile writes.

